query:
INSERT INTO trade (
                            market_id,
                            buyer_id,
                            seller_id,
                            transaction_id,
                            size,
                            price,
                            buyer_is_taker
                        ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
                        RETURNING
                            id as "id!",
                            market_id,
                            buyer_id,
                            seller_id,
                            transaction_id,
                            size as "size: _",
                            price as "price: _",
                            ? as "transaction_timestamp!: _",
                            buyer_is_taker as "buyer_is_taker: _"
